_main_2527589\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fnk1665702757456.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fnk1665702757456.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fnk1665702757456.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fnk1665702757456\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Extracting Values From Numeric Data\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__extracting_values_from_numeric_data_53942\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">When you are working with data stored as a Numeric or Float value, you can extract information such as the integer part or the fractional part of a value. This extraction is done with a numeric extraction parameter.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__p_d16232e1_d16233e1_d16234e1\">The format for using numeric extraction is:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__p_d16235e1_d16236e1_d16237e1\">(<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">Variable</var> ) <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">[</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Parameter</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">]</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Numeric Extraction Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__2\">\n Data extracted\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">trunc</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">I</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__2\">\n Integer part of the value.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">fraction</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__2\">\n Fractional part of the value.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">round</code>{,<var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var>} | <code class=\"ph codeph\">R</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fnk1665702757456__table_d1706e1_d1707e1_d1708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Rounded value of a number, where <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> is an integer that indicates the decimal place to which you want to round the value.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__li_d7658e1_d7659e1_d7660e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> &lt; 0, round to <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> positions left of the decimal point.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__li_d7661e1_d7662e1_d7663e1\">if <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> &gt; 0, round to <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> positions right of the decimal point.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__li_d7664e1_d7665e1_d7666e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> = 0 or omitted, round to the nearest unit.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__note_w3090ab1b5b7b3b7b5b3b5_w3091ab1b5b7b3b7b5b3_w3092ab1b5b7b3b7b5_w3093ab1b5b7b3b7_w3094ab1b5b7b3_w3095ab1b5b7_w3096ab1b5_w3097ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If the fixed number of decimal digits after the decimal point\n                        is explicitly set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> in <var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var> (that\n                        is, the number is an integer) it is not rounded, to preserve integer\n                        arithmetic.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__section_xy5_qsw_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d733349e199\">Example: Fraction and Truncate</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__p_d16241e1_d16242e1_d16243e1\">The following code shows the effect of numeric\n            extraction parameters on a value.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__pre_uys_rsw_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n numeric vSource, vFraction, vTrunc, vCalc\nendvariables\nvSource = 123.76\nvFraction = vSource [fraction] ; vFraction = 0.76\nvTrunc = vSource [trunc] ; vTrunc = 123\nvCalc = vSource[trunc]+.11 ; vCalc = 123.11</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__section_gnw_4sw_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d733349e212\">Example: Rounding</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__p_d16247e1_d16248e1_d16249e1\">The following code shows the effect of the value of\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> on rounding:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fnk1665702757456__pre_swk_psw_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n numeric vRounded , vRoundedA, vRoundedB, vRoundedC \nendvariables\nvSource = 1897.7652\nvRounded = vSource[round] ; vRounded = 1898\nvRoundedA = vSource[round,0] ; vRoundedA = 1898\nvRoundedB = vSource[round,-2] ; vRoundedB = 1900\nvRoundedC = vSource[round,2] ; vRoundedC = 1897.77\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527589\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527589\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Extracting Values From Numeric Data Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Extracting Values From Numeric Data When you are working with data stored as a Numeric or Float value, you can extract information such as the integer part or the fractional part of a value. This extraction is done with a numeric extraction parameter. The format for using numeric extraction is: ( Field | Variable ) = Source [ Parameter ] Table 1. Numeric Extraction Parameters Parameter Data extracted trunc | I Integer part of the value. fraction | F Fractional part of the value. round {, n } | R Rounded value of a number, where n is an integer that indicates the decimal place to which you want to round the value. If n < 0, round to n positions left of the decimal point. if n > 0, round to n positions right of the decimal point. If n = 0 or omitted, round to the nearest unit. Note: If the fixed number of decimal digits after the decimal point is explicitly set to 0 in Source (that is, the number is an integer) it is not rounded, to preserve integer arithmetic. Example: Fraction and Truncate The following code shows the effect of numeric extraction parameters on a value. variables numeric vSource, vFraction, vTrunc, vCalc endvariables vSource = 123.76 vFraction = vSource [fraction] ; vFraction = 0.76 vTrunc = vSource [trunc] ; vTrunc = 123 vCalc = vSource[trunc]+.11 ; vCalc = 123.11 Copy Example: Rounding The following code shows the effect of the value of n on rounding: variables numeric vRounded , vRoundedA, vRoundedB, vRoundedC endvariables vSource = 1897.7652 vRounded = vSource[round] ; vRounded = 1898 vRoundedA = vSource[round,0] ; vRoundedA = 1898 vRoundedB = vSource[round,-2] ; vRoundedB = 1900 vRoundedC = vSource[round,2] ; vRoundedC = 1897.77 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}